{"tid":1442503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【聚焦五大訴求】人民網：逐一反駁「五大訴求」 指法律須露出鋒利牙齒","createTime":"2019-08-11T03:36:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T04:01:32.000Z","uid":173207,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f80311eec042a24961ec9430428116f15805382a","tid":1442503,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:36:30.000Z","msg":"一定要好好咁聚焦五大訴求，唔好再失焦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\nRTHK<br />\n人民網：逐一反駁「五大訴求」 指法律須露出鋒利牙齒 2019-08-11 HKT07:43<br />\n<br />\n人民網發表文章，逐一反駁「五大訴求」。（胡兆榮攝）<br />\n內地人民網評論香港局勢，認為香港要止暴制亂，法律須要露出鋒利牙齒。<br />\n<br />\n評論表示，警方嚴正執法是第一步，法官嚴正司法是第二步，在懲治暴徒一事上，警方和法官才是真正的命運共同體。評論認為，讓整個社會染上焦躁，陷入撕裂，法官也開始遭受謾罵和侮辱，不是司法機關想要的局面，能接受的局面。<br />\n<br />\n評論又談到示威者提出的五大訴求，認為「撤回」是偽命題，「取消暴動定性」是指鹿為馬，「要求特赦」是天方夜譚，「成立獨立調查委員會」是圍點打援，「全面落實雙普選」是不知魏晉，忘記歷史，歪曲現實，踐踏法治，褻瀆香港核心價值，香港社會有共識，不答應，香港市民心水清，不會上當。<br />\n<br />\n評論又強調，底線就是底線，退無可退觸碰了底線，必須響起警報;此般惡劣犯罪情形，沒有妥協和姑息空間。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473926-20190811.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473926-20190811.htm&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbU2WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=68265be3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473926-20190811.htm&h=596d4ac3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473926-20190811.htm</a>"},{"pid":"45262802ded2090d051bf5166628fe901f33a635","tid":1442503,"uid":151796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:37:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e64cf99dfcc5a47f44dc7feabc3cea233d80ed7d","tid":1442503,"uid":290176,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:37:48.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">官鄉警黑721 <br />\n變本加厲810</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"d7c63f389dd5889541f68e819eb8aac52f437fdf","tid":1442503,"uid":192776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b896bf771b3ddf8a6db2baa950c86e59a8cbd2","tid":1442503,"uid":37081,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:38:04.000Z","msg":"邊有逐一反駁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n逐一批評昨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a88128391475998a5e58d9da52c371897c925785","tid":1442503,"uid":173207,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:39:30.000Z","msg":"官媒喉舌特登為五大訴求呢到去整篇文 即係話五大訴求好緊要 各位一定要記得記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"504812d9289b46c3e8d25bf20b8160f6055433cb","tid":1442503,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:40:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f3a7b4cc1ed660456aa75d9258a91a2b8929d1ea","tid":1442503,"uid":164730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:40:05.000Z","msg":"吓，小學雞嘈交就叫反駁？？？"},{"pid":"1d454ec6f8ddbbd9f5e2c3e069b1db031c1b854e","tid":1442503,"uid":188176,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:40:19.000Z","msg":"是但塞D四字成語出黎都唔知佢講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f57453f7447c8382c8add9e880b1545556b20548","tid":1442503,"uid":247032,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:41:18.000Z","msg":"又係呢d內容空洞 毫無邏輯理據"},{"pid":"fb50ed56588e40c622adccceb79fbfa782b62e13","tid":1442503,"uid":274722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:41:38.000Z","msg":"「撤回」是偽命題，「取消暴動定性」是指鹿為馬，「要求特赦」是天方夜譚，「成立獨立調查委員會」是圍點打援<br />\n<br />\n呢四個訴求得幾個字屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「全面落實雙普選」是不知魏晉，忘記歷史，歪曲現實，踐踏法治，褻瀆香港核心價值，香港社會有共識，不答應，香港市民心水清，不會上當"},{"pid":"15315af8c8b3b3bbf8c38dfce03f1ddcfad5ac08","tid":1442503,"uid":125258,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:41:57.000Z","msg":"「全面落實雙普選」是不知魏晉，忘記歷史，歪曲現實，踐踏法治，褻瀆香港核心價值<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係狂撻四字成語就代表有道理架<br />\nUp成段野都不知所云"},{"pid":"a92f147634573a88fbeb9ecc77eb33fc8d70fcd3","tid":1442503,"uid":51720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:42:05.000Z","msg":"法律需要露出(鋒利牙齒) -&gt; <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b750f837d9ff21382b9b3fa506bec133e83557b7","tid":1442503,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a92f147634573a88fbeb9ecc77eb33fc8d70fcd3","tid":1442503,"uid":51720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:42:05.000Z","msg":"法律需要露出(鋒利牙齒) -&gt; <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:43:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5fc495887bd7ce0ad63e23d179c5052c80e64d","tid":1442503,"uid":47311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:43:38.000Z","msg":"咩叫不知魏晉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3051c4ff1249e1f5ed0715d40f171ecf5cd69da","tid":1442503,"uid":23060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a92f147634573a88fbeb9ecc77eb33fc8d70fcd3","tid":1442503,"uid":51720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:42:05.000Z","msg":"法律需要露出(鋒利牙齒) -&gt; <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:45:54.000Z","msg":"所以話支那啲法律係用來壓制異見，支持支共話之你殺人放火，仲污染香港。"},{"pid":"0eb60fda0c3afa7b6dbf1ab861bd22a484cde96e","tid":1442503,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:46:24.000Z","msg":"篇文嘅原文：<br />\n<br />\n人民快評：止暴制亂，法律必須露出鋒利的牙齒&mdash;&mdash;二議當前香港局勢<br />\n<br />\n張慶波<br />\n<br />\n從遊行示威到暴力衝擊，從口誅筆伐到拳打腳踢，從欺凌普通市民到侮辱國家、民族，香港極端激進分子一次次邁入法治的禁區，突破一條條底線，用製造的件件樁樁的刑事案件為自己打上了&ldquo;暴徒&rdquo;的標籤，坐實了自己就是法治之敵、和平之敵、市民之敵。<br />\n<br />\n底線歷來清晰。 &ldquo;任何危害國家主權安全、挑戰中央權力和香港特別行政區基本法權威、利用香港對內地進行滲透破壞的活動，都是對底線的觸碰，都是絕不能允許的。&rdquo;明知不可而為之，還要大膽觸碰底線，極端激進分子的行徑只有一種解釋：他們的挑戰是故意的、挑釁是認真的，其所欲所求就是想顛覆底線、摧毀憲制秩序、推翻箝制他們發起&ldquo;顏色革命&rdquo;的一切屏障。<br />\n<br />\n從6月12日在立法會前發起暴力衝擊，到7月1日闖入立法會肆意破壞，再到7月14日在沙田城市廣場群毆警察、7月21日圍攻香港中聯辦、8月5日在香港各區與市民和警察全面對抗，這些極端激進分子展現出其蓄謀已久的一面，有組織、有步驟的一面。他們在復雜的形勢下興風作浪，利用警方的克制得寸進尺，借助營造的&ldquo;黑色恐怖&rdquo;抑制&ldquo;沉默的大多數&rdquo;，企圖用謠言和騷亂把社會的各個方面都裹挾進來，幻想著把整個香港變成他們的戰車並控制她疾速、準確地向懸崖滑去。在黑衣蒙面下，被暴力和野心武裝起來的他們，就是要一條道走到黑，把香港變成他們違法作亂的&ldquo;特區&rdquo;、沒有原則底線的&ldquo;特區&rdquo;、方便他們這些魑魅魍魎橫行無忌的&ldquo;特區&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n在所謂&ldquo;五大訴求&rdquo;包裝下，極端激進分子或以為自己代表著&ldquo;民意&rdquo; ，這種虛妄的認知無疑也屬於意淫。其&ldquo;五大訴求&rdquo;，&ldquo;撤回&rdquo;是偽命題，&ldquo;取消暴動定性&rdquo;是指鹿為馬，&ldquo;要求特赦&rdquo;是天方夜譚，&ldquo;成立獨立調查委員會&rdquo;是圍點打援，&ldquo;全面落實雙普選&rdquo;是不知魏晉，忘記歷史、歪曲現實，踐踏法治、褻瀆香港核心價值，香港社會有共識、不答應，香港市民心水清、不會上當。法治秩序、憲制秩序這些阻擋他們野心氾濫、暴力肆虐的閘門，不僅絕不能搬開，而且一定要嚴防死守、加固築堤。<br />\n<br />\n底線就是底線，退無可退。觸碰了底線，必須響起警報；突破了底線，必須打回去。香港的下限不容刷新，自由的規矩無論何時都要立得住。極端激進分子曾經一時得意，不過是吸毒後的亢奮、犯科後的僥倖，是終究要現​​原形、被鞭撻的。這種大是大非問題，沒有模糊和狡辯可能；此般惡劣犯罪情形，沒有妥協和姑息空間。<br />\n<br />\n警方嚴正執法是第一步，法官嚴正司法是第二步。在懲治暴徒一事上，警方和法官才是真正的命運共同體。 &ldquo;皮之不存，毛將焉附&rdquo;，動搖了法治的根基，司法機關豈能獨善其身！非法&ldquo;佔中&rdquo;案審判期間，有法官指出，所謂&ldquo;違法達義&rdquo;煽惑起一種歪風邪氣。讓整個社會染上焦躁、陷入撕裂，法官也開始遭受謾罵和侮辱，不是司法機關想要的局面、能接受的局面。 &ldquo;這邊抓、那邊放&rdquo;的情況，&ldquo;一波尚未平息，一波又要興起&rdquo;的情況，那些削足適履、掘墓自焚的情況，不應再出現在擁有良好法治傳統的香港。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;誰是我們的敵人？誰是我們的朋友？&rdquo;已再清楚不過。底線就擺在那裡，社會最大公約數就擺在那裡，民心民意就擺在那裡，在&ldquo;沉默的大多數&rdquo;都不再沉默之後，在警方不顧個人安危、傾心傾力為家園守護之時，在法官敲下公義之鎚、向違法事件亮劍的過程中，極端激進分子還會任性狂妄嗎，暴力欺凌還會有市場嗎，文明之香港、繁華之香港、未來之香港還會受此侵擾、再經磨難嗎？邪不壓正的鐵律，永遠生效、亙古不移，刻在香港歷史恥辱柱上的，只會是他們。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年08月09日19:27&nbsp;&nbsp;來源：人民網-觀點頻道<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://opinion.people.com.cn/n1/2019/0809/c1003-31286726.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fopinion.people.com.cn%2Fn1%2F2019%2F0809%2Fc1003-31286726.html&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbU2WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=308fdbd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://opinion.people.com.cn/n1/2019/0809/c1003-31286726.html</a>"},{"pid":"8e1f9bba8673e989f0f94cd2260fb48e6982c8b8","tid":1442503,"uid":304090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:47:37.000Z","msg":"警黑露出鋒利牙齒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eebc2b510a612608a8d27797d4e03b0c0774c9e","tid":1442503,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:48:26.000Z","msg":"法律人人平等 唔係政府話事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be0c35f956d78bbd26a3626df660c